'''FC Matanzas''' is a [[Cuba]]n [[football (soccer)|football]] club based in [[Matanzas]]. Its home stadium is the 1,000-capacity Estadio Calimete.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://int.soccerway.com/teams/cuba/matanzas/9901/ |title=FC Matanzas |website=Soccerway |publisher=Perform Group |accessdate=1 April 2015}}</ref> It last played in the [[Campeonato Nacional de Fútbol de Cuba|Campeonato Nacional]] in 2013.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rsssf.com/tablesc/cuba2013.html |title=Cuba 2013 |first=Karel |last=Stokkermans |publisher=Rec.Sport.Soccer Statistics Foundation (RSSSF) |date=13 February 2014 |accessdate=1 April 2015}}</ref>

